tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE VehicleMileage (
    vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    mileage INT,
    last_maintenance_date DATE,
    next_maintenance_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE Vehicle (
    vehicle_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    manufacturer VARCHAR(255),
    model VARCHAR(255),
    year INT,
    mileage INT
);

CREATE TABLE Maintenance (
    maintenance_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id UUID REFERENCES Vehicle(vehicle_id),
    maintenance_type VARCHAR(255),
    maintenance_date DATE,
    mileage_at_maintenance INT
);

CREATE TABLE Replacement (
    replacement_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id UUID REFERENCES Vehicle(vehicle_id),
    replacement_type VARCHAR(255),
    replacement_date DATE,
    mileage_at_replacement INT
);

CREATE TABLE ServiceHistory (
    service_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id UUID REFERENCES Vehicle(vehicle_id),
    service_type VARCHAR(255),
    service_date DATE,
    mileage_at_service INT
);

CREATE TABLE MaintenanceHistory (
   maintenance_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
   vehicle_id INTEGER REFERENCES Vehicle(vehicle_id),
   maintenance_type VARCHAR(50),
   maintenance_date DATE,
   cost DECIMAL(10, 2)
);
